desc.text: I am a front-end web developer living in Williamsburg, Virginia. What started as an inquisition into programming languages in order to gain more skills in report automation for my job as a Sales Manager, quickly became an obsession for developing fun and interactive applications!
Programming with Ruby on Rails and PHP, SASS and UX Design
I'm constantly learning and exploring new ways to increase my skills to enhance my work. I love discovering a tool or technique and seeing it come to life in the project I am creating.
hiking, quilting, reading, baking, traveling, playing with sasha my beagle.
